    &gt;Install Proxmox VE on Debian 12 Bookworm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://wiki.debian.org/SourcesList&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Debian SourcesList&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
